{"type": "article", "id": 7411, "title": "奥林巴斯数码相机", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-16T07:21:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234442CEwsH3i4TNSXu1RI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t上周，奥林巴斯推出了最新款的复古 Stylus SH-2 数码相机，其定位是旅行摄影高端便携相机，这款相机和复古 PEN 系列无反相似。使用 24 倍光学变焦镜头，48 倍超精细变焦，实现 25mm 广角端到 600mm 长焦端变焦范围。另外，在防抖和夜间拍摄上此次 SH-2 也有进步和创新，另加了 Raw 格式支持，基本满足旅行摄影的需求。黑色机身，银色铝合金顶端操控面，看起来简洁大方。目前这款相机定价是约 2500 元人民币，预计四月份开卖。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234438lDb1FnouNHLSdKWA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74449878\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234439BER5VUSzrvPs1IW3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.6797066\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234439Plv5TdkKE9iY3fHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71882641\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344404AqtOQJT5Hj13Sni.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.60757946\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052344415xD3NRXtlsGjQVgI.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59290954\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t